支那app個玩法係咪直頭好似有個人喺你格離睇咁<br />\n咁中間份包裹點加密都冇用架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"其實咩app都好，可能只係自稱佢幫你加密，無人肯定到到佢有無做。所以先最好用啲源碼開源app。如果你唔小心下載個陣allow 曬啲permission，佢就可以長期睇住你做緊啲咩。<br />\n而家啲裸聊，叫人裝佢個app 都係一樣道理，佢個app 會偷曬你啲資料。"},{"pid":"976a542d64cfc8426b18431f1e387b6ed441c6b9","tid":2364903,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"用 windows 同 mac 之後擔心資料被偷"},{"pid":"13f3276edd25fa0057bbde33519eeee5f6064ef6","tid":2364903,"uid":9248,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6e705efc37fb266509045e0e2cdb0d7f5d682b79","tid":2364903,"uid":134087,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn4.geckoandfly.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/end-to-end-encryption-comparison-decentralized.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn4.geckoandfly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fend-to-end-encryption-comparison-decentralized.jpg&h=49417f80&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:08:09.000Z","msg":"點解 case 1唔算 E2EE?<br />\n如果你 client side encrypt 咗<br />\nISP 點都唔會睇到"},{"pid":"2a03c99d9e89dd3acabf4870121f073525d37fd2","tid":2364903,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:36:29.000Z","msg":"即係個app 用收件人個數碼鎖幫你加密左封信<br />\n只有收件人先有鎖匙解密睇到<br />\n<br />\n你上面講係指封信未入信封已經比人睇晒<br />\n<br />\n呢層就要睇個os (kernal)有無漏洞可以比另一個app 睇到其他app 的在ram 入面的資料<br />\n<br />\n去到最底層<br />\n你打緊既字 只係 中ram 入面某個位用一種特既1同0排列組合代表緊 理論上你有岩既器材同知道部機器行到咩狀態就揾到<br />\n<br />\n亦有新聞話可以靠電子流動發微小電磁波變化去讀 到 d 無連網既電腦既資料添"},{"pid":"3be2a454dd9113a5aa33316bef72abc66e56fed2","tid":2364903,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"messaging 有3方，sender &gt; messager server(s) &gt; receiver<br />\n主要係指個messaging servers 都睇唔到你打乜<br />\n唔係指其他app 睇唔睇到"},{"pid":"d209562a5c63e8ce51ca254451c